(42, 1, 17, 13, 29, 18, 18, NULL, 'Preparation of Hearts', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of preparing hearts for God. Luke 1:17 speaks of making ready a people prepared for the Lord, while 1 Chronicles 29:18 requests that God prepare their heart unto thee.', 'theme', 0.377, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
